OL,3,CSecretary of State: Increase in
OL,4,Cminimum wage will be 'real help'
OL,6,FHe said: "Today is really good news
OL,7,Ffor 170,000 people in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fwho get to see the national living
OL,9,Fwage and the national minimum wage
OL,10,Fincrease, and for a low-paid, full-
OL,11,Ftime worker it will mean an additional
OL,12,F#1,400 a year, and that is a big boost
OL,13,Fthat I'm sure will be widely welcomed."
OL,15,FThe changes from April 1 mean the
OL,16,Fnational living wage for those aged 21
OL,17,Fand over will rise from #11.44 per
OL,18,Fhour to #12.21 per hour and for 18 to
OL,19,F20-year-olds from #8.60 to #10.00 per
OL,20,Fhour.
