OL,6,FThe apprenticeship rate, and minimum
OL,7,Fwage for 16 to 17-year-olds, rises
OL,8,Ffrom #6.40 per hour to #7.55 per hour.
OL,10,FThe Government earlier this month
OL,11,Fannounced a tightening of eligibility
OL,12,Ffor the main disability benefit `
OL,13,Fpersonal independence payment (Pip) `
OL,14,Fand changes to the sickness element of
OL,15,Funiversal credit.
OL,17,FChancellor Rachel Reeves also
OL,18,Fconfirmed in last week's spring
OL,19,Fstatement that universal credit health
OL,20,Fbenefits for new claimants will be
OL,21,Fhalved in 2026 and then frozen.
