OL,3,CSecretary of State: Increase in
OL,4,Cminimum wage will be 'real help'
OL,6,FAccording to Stormont's Department for
OL,7,FCommunities in February 2024, there
OL,8,Fwere 205,000 claimants of Pip with 45%
OL,9,Fof claims having a main disabling
OL,10,Fcondition relating to mental illness.
OL,12,FThere is a higher concentration of
OL,13,Fdisability-related benefit claimants
OL,14,Fin Northern Ireland than in Great
OL,15,FBritain, with one in 8.5 of the
OL,16,Fpopulation in the region claiming some
OL,17,Fdisability benefit, compared to one in
OL,18,F17 in GB, according to the Northern
OL,19,FIreland Audit Office.
