OL,3,CSecretary of State: Increase in
OL,4,Cminimum wage will be 'real help'
OL,6,FAsked about the higher proportion of
OL,7,FPip claimants in Northern Ireland, Mr
OL,8,FBenn said: "I think the first thing to
OL,9,Fsay is the economy in Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fis growing faster than the United
OL,11,FKingdom as a whole, and that should be
OL,12,Fa source of great pride to businesses
OL,13,Fand workers in Northern Ireland.
OL,15,F"Secondly, the current welfare system
OL,16,Fisn't sustainable, and it doesn't
OL,17,Factually help people who can get back
OL,18,Finto work to do so, and that's why
OL,19,Fwe're making a number of changes.
